This project has the purpose to build a infra-structure to create IRC-like bots on Facebook.
There is a quiz game included as example, gamagame.py 
http://www.facebook.com/thegamagame

To make it work, first create a fb application following fb tutorial, then create this configuration files:
---- config.php ----
<?php
   $app_id = "APP_ID";
   $app_secret = "APP_SECRET";
   $my_url = "http://localhost/FBOT/index.php";
?>

and

---- config_access_token ----
ACCESS_TOKEN


To get the ACCESS_TOKEN, use the php application in the folder php_get_token

